    • Constructor Detail

      • DataCollectionRealTimeSnapshotSet

        public DataCollectionRealTimeSnapshotSet(PerformanceData performanceData,
                                 int selectSequenceId,
                                 int minutesBack,
                                 boolean includeErrorEventItems,
                                 boolean getErrorEventItemsOnly)
        Create a new initialized instance. This constructor is called by the load test program only.
        Parameters:
        performanceData - the actual performance data of the load test program
        selectSequenceId - select a specific data collection sequence by the ID of the sequence, or pass -1 (minus one) to get all data collection sequences
        minutesBack - relative point of time in the past (in minutes) from which collecting of the measured items starts, or -1 = from the beginning of the load test execution
        includeErrorEventItems - if false then don't include error event items
        getErrorEventItemsOnly - if true then get only error event items
        See Also:
        PerformanceData.getDataCollectionSet(), DataCollectionAbstractItem.ITEM_TYPE_ERROR_EVENT

      • DataCollectionRealTimeSnapshotSet
